'''Statistics Estonia''' ({{lang-et|Statistikaamet}}) is the [[Estonia]]n government agency responsible for producing official [[statistics]] regarding Estonia. It is subordinated the [[Ministry of Finance (Estonia)|Ministry of Finance]].
The agency has approximately 400 employees. The office of the agency is located in [[Tatari]], [[Tallinn]].
